ocation of\nstars along the HB of a GC. Furthermore, we found a number of fast rotators.\nThey are concentrated in a restricted temperature range along the HB of M22.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Jan 2014 08:21:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-03-05"}
