tic centre for various values of the Kerr\nparameter, electric charge and impact factor. In addition, we derive analytic\nexpressions for the Maxwell tensor components for a\nZero-Angular-Momentum-Observer (ZAMO) in the Kerr-Newman-de Sitter spacetime.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Jan 2014 09:30:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Feb 2014 14:56:05 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 9 Feb 2014 11:35:04 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 30 Jun 2014 09:35:58 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 26 Feb 2015 08:33:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-27"}
